.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-INVOICE-PAID-COUNT-TODAY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-invoice-paid-count-today \- FEAT-2504 count of invoices paid today (paid_at within last 24h)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-invoice-paid-count-today
.SH DESCRIPTION
node-invoice-paid-count-today for lightning CLI (FEAT-2504).
.PP
Returns the number of invoices with status paid and paid_at within the last 24 hours.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
